General.Name: Bioservo Technologies AB
General.Description: Bioservo Technologies AB (publ) develops and sells wearable muscle strengthening systems worldwide. The company offers Ironhand, a robotic grip that strengthens gloves; and Carbonhand, a revolutionary assistive device for people with impaired hand function. Its products have applications in foundry, logistics, warehousing, and construction sectors, as well as used in pre-assembly and assembly tasks. The company was incorporated in 2003 and is based in Kista, Sweden.
